gap_y 24
no_buffers yes
alignment top_right
text_buffer_size 1080
TEXT
WINDOW MANAGEMENT
${hr}
Alt+F4 - Close
Alt+F7 - Move
Alt+F8 - Resize

Super+m - Maximize
Super+i - Iconify
Super+r - 50% width, center
Super+Shift+a - toggle autoshade
Super+Shift+t - toggle always on top
Super+Shift+d - undecorate
Super+d - decorate
Super+Shift+arrow - move titlebar
Super+Shift+{1..3} - add window to group
Super+{1..3} - switch windows/groups

LAUNCH APPLICATIONS
${hr}
Launch app/go to window/switch app windows
Super+t - terminal
Super+f - file manager
Super+e - text editor
Super+w - web browser
Super+p - music player

Ctrl+Super+key to launch app whatsoever

OTHER STUFF
${hr}
PrtScr - take screenshot
Super+Space - main menu
Ctrl+Grave - quake-terminal
Alt+m - fvwm console
Alt+F2 - run application


